com.siperian.sif.message.metadata

Class MetaDataHmTypeBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataBase
      • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataHmTypeBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MetaDataHmEntityType, MetaDataHmRelationshipType

    public class MetaDataHmTypeBase
extends MetaDataBase
    Represents the base class for MetaDataHmRelationshipType and MetaDataHmEntityType. All common functionality is provided by this class. This class is never instantiated on its own and is accessed only through a subclass.
    See Also:
    DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form

    API Group: Metadata
